## purpose
Defines the canonical architectural role of legal in CivilizationOS.

## design_intent
Legal is the bounded formal-rule structure
through which lawful validity,
procedure,
claim,
decision,
and enforceable interpretation
become meaningful.

## canonical_rules
- legal claim is not final legal determination
- legal procedure must remain attributable
- historical legal trace must remain queryable
- ambiguous legal validity fails closed
